data.description: Enjoy peaceful settings in this Immaculate Home situated on almost an acre! This home  shows pride of ownership and features 3 bdrms and a den or can be 4th bedroom. Enjoy the early morning sunrises or beautiful sunsets and spectacular mountain views all around.  All tile throughout, (no carpet), a brand new roof, split floorplan, kitchen and dining combo, and a large storage shed. This is a must see! Only appx 15 minutes away from Bisbee in one direction and 25 minutes from Sierra Vista in the opposite direction. VA Assumable Loan at 3.25% interest rate option is available.
